{"id": 1717, "title": "Ticket #1717: don't invoke glexec if the proxy is expired to avoid the overhead.", "description": "<blockquote>\nInvoking glexec has some overhead both on the local machine and on the LCAS server.  It is guaranteed to fail if an expired proxy is used to invoke glexec, so check the proxy first and just skip glexec entirely if the proxy is not valid.</blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2010-Oct-20 10:58</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/e74331f86f7e6e9728bd55662fbf8758aae113a5\">[25745]</a></span>: Add entry for glexec fix. <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=1717\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('1717'); return false;\" title=\"don't invoke glexec if the proxy is expired to avoid the overhead.\">#1717</a></span>  (By Jaime Frey )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2010-Oct-17 17:25</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/3ba6b0bc370c7ff3c26acd3b4d3a443f2be1f1fa\">[19180]</a></span>: skip the calling of glexec if the proxy to be used is not valid. (<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=1717\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('1717'); return false;\" title=\"don't invoke glexec if the proxy is expired to avoid the overhead.\">#1717</a></span>)  (By Zach Miller )</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>", "type": "enhance", "last